{
  "video_id": "LI8ix9IghkY",
  "title": "Karen Bass: Unseen footage, untamed nature",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 16010.000000000002,
      "text": "Translator: Timothy Covell Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16010.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19319.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a very lucky person."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19319.0,
      "end_time": 23797.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been privileged to see so much of our beautiful Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23797.0,
      "end_time": 26125.0,
      "text": "and the people and creatures that live on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26125.0,
      "end_time": 29745.0,
      "text": "And my passion was inspired at the age of seven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29745.0,
      "end_time": 32080.0,
      "text": "when my parents first took me to Morocco,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32080.0,
      "end_time": 34206.0,
      "text": "at the edge of the Sahara Desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34206.0,
      "end_time": 36581.0,
      "text": "Now imagine a little Brit"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36581.0,
      "end_time": 39702.0,
      "text": "somewhere that wasn&#39;t cold and damp like home."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39702.0,
      "end_time": 41978.0,
      "text": "What an amazing experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41978.0,
      "end_time": 44471.0,
      "text": "And it made me want to explore more."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44471.0,
      "end_time": 47074.0,
      "text": "So as a filmmaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47074.0,
      "end_time": 49885.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been from one end of the Earth to the other"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49885.0,
      "end_time": 52593.0,
      "text": "trying to get the perfect shot"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52593.0,
      "end_time": 56385.0,
      "text": "and to capture animal behavior never seen before."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56385.0,
      "end_time": 59017.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s more, I&#39;m really lucky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59017.0,
      "end_time": 62135.0,
      "text": "because I get to share that with millions of people worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62135.0,
      "end_time": 67385.0,
      "text": "Now the idea of having new perspectives of our planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67385.0,
      "end_time": 71218.0,
      "text": "and actually being able to get that message out"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71218.0,
      "end_time": 74076.0,
      "text": "gets me out of bed every day with a spring in my step."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74076.0,
      "end_time": 77218.0,
      "text": "You might think that it&#39;s quite hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77218.0,
      "end_time": 79468.0,
      "text": "to find new stories and new subjects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79468.0,
      "end_time": 83799.0,
      "text": "but new technology is changing the way we can film."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83799.0,
      "end_time": 87635.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s enabling us to get fresh, new images"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87635.0,
      "end_time": 89752.0,
      "text": "and tell brand new stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89752.0,
      "end_time": 92635.0,
      "text": "In Nature&#39;s Great Events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92635.0,
      "end_time": 96177.0,
      "text": "a series for the BBC that I did with David Attenborough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96177.0,
      "end_time": 98427.0,
      "text": "we wanted to do just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98427.0,
      "end_time": 101468.0,
      "text": "Images of grizzly bears are pretty familiar."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101468.0,
      "end_time": 104718.0,
      "text": "You see them all the time, you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104718.0,
      "end_time": 108802.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a whole side to their lives that we hardly ever see"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108802.0,
      "end_time": 110510.0,
      "text": "and had never been filmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110510.0,
      "end_time": 114760.0,
      "text": "So what we did, we went to Alaska,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114760.0,
      "end_time": 117128.0,
      "text": "which is where the grizzlies rely"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117128.0,
      "end_time": 120114.0,
      "text": "on really high, almost inaccessible, mountain slopes"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120114.0,
      "end_time": 122049.0,
      "text": "for their denning."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122049.0,
      "end_time": 129564.0,
      "text": "And the only way to film that is a shoot from the air."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129564.0,
      "end_time": 134177.0,
      "text": "(Video) David Attenborough: Throughout Alaska and British Columbia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 134177.0,
      "end_time": 139389.0,
      "text": "thousands of bear families are emerging from their winter sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139389.0,
      "end_time": 143343.0,
      "text": "There is nothing to eat up here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143343.0,
      "end_time": 146843.0,
      "text": "but the conditions were ideal for hibernation."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146843.0,
      "end_time": 154710.0,
      "text": "Lots of snow in which to dig a den."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 154710.0,
      "end_time": 160700.0,
      "text": "To find food, mothers must lead their cubs down to the coast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 160700.0,
      "end_time": 167762.0,
      "text": "where the snow will already be melting."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 167762.0,
      "end_time": 200983.0,
      "text": "But getting down can be a challenge for small cubs."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 200983.0,
      "end_time": 204718.0,
      "text": "These mountains are dangerous places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 204718.0,
      "end_time": 208177.0,
      "text": "but ultimately the fate of these bear families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 208177.0,
      "end_time": 211691.0,
      "text": "and indeed that of all bears around the North Pacific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 211691.0,
      "end_time": 216324.0,
      "text": "depends on the salmon."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 216324.0,
      "end_time": 218885.0,
      "text": "KB: I love that shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 218885.0,
      "end_time": 221177.0,
      "text": "I always get goosebumps every time I see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 221177.0,
      "end_time": 223218.0,
      "text": "That was filmed from a helicopter"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 223218.0,
      "end_time": 226010.0,
      "text": "using a gyro-stabilized camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 226010.0,
      "end_time": 228468.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a wonderful bit of gear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 228468.0,
      "end_time": 232427.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s like having a flying tripod, crane and dolly all rolled into one."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 232427.0,
      "end_time": 235635.0,
      "text": "But technology alone isn&#39;t enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 235635.0,
      "end_time": 238135.0,
      "text": "To really get the money shots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 238135.0,
      "end_time": 241177.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s down to being in the right place at the right time."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 241177.0,
      "end_time": 244135.0,
      "text": "And that sequence was especially difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 244135.0,
      "end_time": 247635.0,
      "text": "The first year we got nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 247635.0,
      "end_time": 251218.0,
      "text": "We had to go back the following year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 251218.0,
      "end_time": 254218.0,
      "text": "all the way back to the remote parts of Alaska."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 254218.0,
      "end_time": 256843.0,
      "text": "And we hung around with a helicopter for two whole weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 256843.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259885.00000000003,
      "text": "And eventually we got lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 259885.0,
      "end_time": 264218.0,
      "text": "The cloud lifted, the wind was still,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 264218.0,
      "end_time": 265968.0,
      "text": "and even the bear showed up."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 265968.0,
      "end_time": 268552.0,
      "text": "And we managed to get that magic moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 268552.0,
      "end_time": 270427.0,
      "text": "For a filmmaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 270427.0,
      "end_time": 274600.0,
      "text": "new technology is an amazing tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 274600.0,
      "end_time": 277806.0,
      "text": "but the other thing that really, really excites me"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 277806.0,
      "end_time": 280760.0,
      "text": "is when new species are discovered."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 280760.0,
      "end_time": 283047.0,
      "text": "Now, when I heard about one animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 283047.0,
      "end_time": 286010.0,
      "text": "I knew we had to get it for my next series,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 286010.0,
      "end_time": 288760.0,
      "text": "Untamed Americas, for National Geographic."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 288760.0,
      "end_time": 295071.0,
      "text": "In 2005, a new species of bat was discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 295071.0,
      "end_time": 297343.0,
      "text": "in the cloud forests of Ecuador."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 297343.0,
      "end_time": 299427.0,
      "text": "And what was amazing about that discovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 299427.0,
      "end_time": 301843.0,
      "text": "is that it also solved the mystery"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 301843.0,
      "end_time": 304880.0,
      "text": "of what pollinated a unique flower."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 304880.0,
      "end_time": 306843.0,
      "text": "It depends solely on the bat."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 306843.0,
      "end_time": 309577.0,
      "text": "Now, the series hasn&#39;t even aired yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 309577.0,
      "end_time": 312004.0,
      "text": "so you&#39;re the very first to see this."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 312004.0,
      "end_time": 316850.0,
      "text": "See what you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 316850.0,
      "end_time": 325796.0,
      "text": "(Video) Narrator: The tube-lipped nectar bat."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 325796.0,
      "end_time": 328137.0,
      "text": "A pool of delicious nectar"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 328137.0,
      "end_time": 330302.0,
      "text": "lies at the bottom of each flower&#39;s long flute."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 330302.0,
      "end_time": 335147.0,
      "text": "But how to reach it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 335147.0,
      "end_time": 340343.0,
      "text": "Necessity is the mother of evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 340343.0,
      "end_time": 363749.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 363749.0,
      "end_time": 366756.0,
      "text": "This two-and-a-half-inch bat"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 366756.0,
      "end_time": 373481.0,
      "text": "has a three-and-a-half-inch tongue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 373481.0,
      "end_time": 377379.0,
      "text": "the longest relative to body length"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 377379.0,
      "end_time": 379698.0,
      "text": "of any mammal in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 379698.0,
      "end_time": 391382.0,
      "text": "If human, he&#39;d have a nine-foot tongue."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 391382.0,
      "end_time": 393872.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 393872.0,
      "end_time": 395937.0,
      "text": "KB: What a tongue."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 395937.0,
      "end_time": 400802.0,
      "text": "We filmed it by cutting a tiny little hole in the base of the flower"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 400802.0,
      "end_time": 405427.0,
      "text": "and using a camera that could slow the action by 40 times."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 405427.0,
      "end_time": 408510.0,
      "text": "So imagine how quick that thing is in real life."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 408510.0,
      "end_time": 413722.0,
      "text": "Now people often ask me, &quot;Where&#39;s your favorite place on the planet?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 413722.0,
      "end_time": 416255.0,
      "text": "And the truth is I just don&#39;t have one."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 416255.0,
      "end_time": 418802.0,
      "text": "There are so many wonderful places."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 418802.0,
      "end_time": 422302.0,
      "text": "But some locations draw you back time and time again."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 422302.0,
      "end_time": 425050.0,
      "text": "And one remote location --"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 425050.0,
      "end_time": 427070.0,
      "text": "I first went there as a backpacker;"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 427070.0,
      "end_time": 429385.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been back several times for filming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 429385.0,
      "end_time": 431135.0,
      "text": "most recently for Untamed Americas --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 431135.0,
      "end_time": 435885.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the Altiplano in the high Andes of South America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 435885.0,
      "end_time": 441052.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the most otherworldly place I know."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 441052.0,
      "end_time": 444154.0,
      "text": "But at 15,000 feet, it&#39;s tough."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 444154.0,
      "end_time": 445677.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s freezing cold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 445677.0,
      "end_time": 450343.0,
      "text": "and that thin air really gets you."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 450343.0,
      "end_time": 452654.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it&#39;s hard to breathe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 452654.0,
      "end_time": 455697.0,
      "text": "especially carrying all the heavy filming equipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 455697.0,
      "end_time": 460302.0,
      "text": "And that pounding head just feels like a constant hangover."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 460302.0,
      "end_time": 464593.0,
      "text": "But the advantage of that wonderful thin atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 464593.0,
      "end_time": 468531.0,
      "text": "is that it enables you to see the stars in the heavens"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 468531.0,
      "end_time": 470970.0,
      "text": "with amazing clarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 470970.0,
      "end_time": 475156.0,
      "text": "Have a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 475156.0,
      "end_time": 478812.0,
      "text": "(Video) Narrator: Some 1,500 miles south of the tropics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 478812.0,
      "end_time": 480497.0,
      "text": "between Chile and Bolivia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 480497.0,
      "end_time": 485673.0,
      "text": "the Andes completely change."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 485673.0,
      "end_time": 490302.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called the Altiplano, or &quot;high plains&quot; --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 490302.0,
      "end_time": 494185.0,
      "text": "a place of extremes"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 494185.0,
      "end_time": 497874.0,
      "text": "and extreme contrasts."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 497874.0,
      "end_time": 502385.0,
      "text": "Where deserts freeze"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 502385.0,
      "end_time": 506218.0,
      "text": "and waters boil."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 506218.0,
      "end_time": 509718.0,
      "text": "More like Mars than Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 509718.0,
      "end_time": 520456.0,
      "text": "it seems just as hostile to life."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 520456.0,
      "end_time": 530325.0,
      "text": "The stars themselves --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 530325.0,
      "end_time": 534046.0,
      "text": "at 12,000 feet, the dry, thin air"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 534046.0,
      "end_time": 542189.0,
      "text": "makes for perfect stargazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 542189.0,
      "end_time": 548073.0,
      "text": "Some of the world&#39;s astronomers have telescopes nearby."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 548073.0,
      "end_time": 552145.0,
      "text": "But just looking up with the naked eye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 552145.0,
      "end_time": 555390.0,
      "text": "you really don&#39;t need one."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 555390.0,
      "end_time": 602400.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
